        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Create a blog using this data:\nTitle: {{ $json.title }}\nMain Topic: {{ $json[\"Main Idea / Topic\"] }}\nSEO Keywords: {{ $json[\"SEO Keywords \"] }}\nImage Hint: {{ $json[\"image prompt\"] }}\nInstructions:\nWrite an engaging intro.\nAdd clear headings and sections.\nUse keywords naturally.\nEnd with a short conclusion.\nReturn output in this format:\n{\n  \"blog_title\": \"string\",\n  \"blog_body\": \"string\",\n  \"image_prompt\": \"string\"\n}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are an expert content writer and SEO specialist. Your task is to create high-quality, detailed, and engaging blog posts for WordPress. \n- Use the main keyword and secondary keywords naturally.\n- Create a clear structure: Introduction, Explanation, Detailed Sections, Examples, and Conclusion.\n- Provide actionable insights where possible.\n- Write in a professional but reader-friendly style.\n- Ensure content is original and descriptive.\n- Output only valid JSON according to this schema:\n{\n  \"title\": \"string\",\n  \"slug\": \"string\",\n  \"meta_description\": \"string\",\n  \"sections\": [\n    {\n      \"heading\": \"string\",\n      \"paragraphs\": [\"string\"]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": [\"string\"]\n}\n- Do NOT include explanations, newlines outside JSON, HTML tags, or extra text.\n- Escape quotes inside strings properly.\n- Always produce this exact JSON structure in every execution.\n"
        }
      },
